{
  "video_id": "iYPifEyFadA",
  "title": "The next global arms race? | The Economist",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 961.0,
      "end_time": 8562.0,
      "text": "President Donald Trump has threatened to pull the plug on one of the most important arms treaties passed 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 8562.0,
      "end_time": 10884.0,
      "text": "One side has not been adhering to it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 10884.0,
      "end_time": 13344.0,
      "text": "we have but one side hasn't."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 13344.0,
      "end_time": 16926.0,
      "text": "Signed in 1987, between Russia and America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16926.0,
      "end_time": 19798.0,
      "text": "the Intermediate-Range Nuclear Forces Treaty"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19798.0,
      "end_time": 23150.0,
      "text": "otherwise known as the INF contributed to the beginning"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 23150.0,
      "end_time": 25300.0,
      "text": "of the end of the Cold War."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25300.0,
      "end_time": 28231.0,
      "text": "For more than a decade, Russia has been cheating the terms"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 28231.0,
      "end_time": 29459.0,
      "text": "of the deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 29459.0,
      "end_time": 32059.0,
      "text": "But what would be the death of the nuclear pact mean"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 32058.999999999996,
      "end_time": 32892.0,
      "text": "for world peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38264.0,
      "end_time": 42011.0,
      "text": "In 1987, after the years of the negotiation"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42011.0,
      "end_time": 44678.0,
      "text": "the super powers agreed to meet."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46633.0,
      "end_time": 51204.0,
      "text": "Today, I for the United States and the General Secretary"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51204.0,
      "end_time": 55289.0,
      "text": "for the Soviet Union have signed the first agreement ever"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55289.0,
      "end_time": 58502.0,
      "text": "to eliminate an entire class of US"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58502.0,
      "end_time": 61214.0,
      "text": "and Soviet nuclear weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61214.0,
      "end_time": 62964.0,
      "text": "We have made history."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64292.0,
      "end_time": 67223.0,
      "text": "Mr. Reagan and Mr. Gorbachev agreed to destroy"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67223.0,
      "end_time": 70391.0,
      "text": "and never again produce land based missiles with a range"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70391.0,
      "end_time": 73684.0,
      "text": "of 500 to 5,500 miles."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73684.0,
      "end_time": 76061.0,
      "text": "Some politicians and journalists"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76061.0,
      "end_time": 79697.0,
      "text": "are already speculating as to who has won."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79697.0,
      "end_time": 81826.0,
      "text": "I reject this approach."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 81826.0,
      "end_time": 85360.0,
      "text": "It is a throwback to old thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 85360.0,
      "end_time": 87939.0,
      "text": "At the time The Economist reported"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 87939.0,
      "end_time": 90080.0,
      "text": "that the world has crossed the Rubicon"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90080.0,
      "end_time": 92037.0,
      "text": "of nuclear disarmament"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 92037.0,
      "end_time": 94271.0,
      "text": "but warned that the west should trend carefully"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94271.0,
      "end_time": 96715.0,
      "text": "because westen public opinion may be lulled"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 96715.0,
      "end_time": 101296.0,
      "text": "into thinking that Russia is no longer an adversary."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 101296.0,
      "end_time": 103417.0,
      "text": "In the Department of Defense, we've viewed Gorbachev"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103417.0,
      "end_time": 105732.0,
      "text": "as someone we could do business with."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105732.0,
      "end_time": 107752.0,
      "text": "He was looking to the future and understood"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107752.0,
      "end_time": 112014.0,
      "text": "it could not be based on confrontation with the west."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 112014.0,
      "end_time": 114623.0,
      "text": "Frank Miller spent 30 years working"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 114623.0,
      "end_time": 116905.0,
      "text": "for the US government on national security"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 116905.0,
      "end_time": 120822.0,
      "text": "and negotiated nuclear deals with the Russians."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 122401.0,
      "end_time": 125739.0,
      "text": "This is what the INF Treaty was all about."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 127872.0,
      "end_time": 130870.0,
      "text": "But 30 years after the landmark treaty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 130870.0,
      "end_time": 135870.0,
      "text": "both sites blame the other for breaking the agreement."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 135879.0,
      "end_time": 138432.0,
      "text": "In 1987 we were looking to work together"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 138432.0,
      "end_time": 140574.0,
      "text": "and there was a spirit of cooperation."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 140574.0,
      "end_time": 141641.0,
      "text": "There is now a spirit"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 141641.0,
      "end_time": 144377.0,
      "text": "of confrontation emanating from Moscow."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 144377.0,
      "end_time": 146500.0,
      "text": "Putin is using his intelligence services"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 146500.0,
      "end_time": 149499.0,
      "text": "in his cyber services to try to disrupt events"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 149499.0,
      "end_time": 152761.0,
      "text": "in the west and today the Russians actually believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 152761.0,
      "end_time": 156879.0,
      "text": "that nuclear weapons are useful weapons of war"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 156879.0,
      "end_time": 160012.0,
      "text": "and certainly they use them all the time as weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 160012.0,
      "end_time": 161983.0,
      "text": "of coercion and intimidation."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 171526.0,
      "end_time": 174440.0,
      "text": "Over the past decade, Russia has been testing"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 174440.0,
      "end_time": 177999.0,
      "text": "and deploying missiles that break the deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 177999.0,
      "end_time": 180290.0,
      "text": "The Russians say that it is America"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 180290.0,
      "end_time": 181885.0,
      "text": "that's broken he treaty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 181885.0,
      "end_time": 185345.0,
      "text": "claiming NATO's defense shield in Romania and Poland"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 185345.0,
      "end_time": 186297.0,
      "text": "has the capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 186297.0,
      "end_time": 190661.0,
      "text": "to fire intermediate-range missiles into Russia."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 190661.0,
      "end_time": 192905.0,
      "text": "Relations between the United States and Russia now"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 192905.0,
      "end_time": 195076.0,
      "text": "are poor and are getting worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 195076.0,
      "end_time": 197906.0,
      "text": "We need to make clear to Mr. Putin that aggression"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 197906.0,
      "end_time": 201234.0,
      "text": "against the United States is not a policy goal"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 201234.0,
      "end_time": 202401.0,
      "text": "he can pursue."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 203460.0,
      "end_time": 205675.0,
      "text": "Both sides have six months to negotiate"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 205675.0,
      "end_time": 207404.0,
      "text": "before the deal is disbanded."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 207404.0,
      "end_time": 209233.0,
      "text": "But if the treaty collapses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 209233.0,
      "end_time": 212205.0,
      "text": "the consequences could be severe."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 212205.0,
      "end_time": 215556.0,
      "text": "Other countries who are not signatories to the INF"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 215556.0,
      "end_time": 218206.0,
      "text": "including China, India, and Israel"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 218206.0,
      "end_time": 220578.0,
      "text": "have been stockpiling missiles."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 220578.0,
      "end_time": 223648.0,
      "text": "The US and Russia may look to catch up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 223648.0,
      "end_time": 226932.0,
      "text": "sparking an arms race that could jeopardize what is left"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 226932.0,
      "end_time": 228875.0,
      "text": "of global arms control."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 228875.0,
      "end_time": 232230.0,
      "text": "Most worryingly, the potential death of the INF"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 232230.0,
      "end_time": 235374.0,
      "text": "has called into question the new start treaty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 235374.0,
      "end_time": 238120.0,
      "text": "a pact between Russia and America that deals"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 238120.0,
      "end_time": 240435.0,
      "text": "with long range nuclear missiles."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 240435.0,
      "end_time": 242008.0,
      "text": "If this is not agreed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 242008.0,
      "end_time": 244601.0,
      "text": "there would be no constraint on the nuclear forces"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 244601.0,
      "end_time": 247236.0,
      "text": "of America and Russia for the first time"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 247236.0,
      "end_time": 248819.0,
      "text": "in almost 50 years."
    }
  ]
}